input:
-- start template query12.tpl query 64 in stream 0
select /* TPC-DS query12.tpl 0.64 */  i_item_id
      ,i_item_desc 
      ,i_category 
      ,i_class 
      ,i_current_price
      ,sum(ws_ext_sales_price) as itemrevenue 
      ,sum(ws_ext_sales_price)*100/sum(sum(ws_ext_sales_price)) over
          (partition by i_class) as revenueratio
from	
	web_sales
    	,item 
    	,date_dim
where 
	ws_item_sk = i_item_sk 
  	and i_category in ('Electronics', 'Shoes', 'Jewelry')
  	and ws_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
	and d_date between cast('2001-06-29' as date) 
				and dateadd(day,30,cast('2001-06-29' as date))
group by 
	i_item_id
        ,i_item_desc 
        ,i_category
        ,i_class
        ,i_current_price
order by 
	i_category
        ,i_class
        ,i_item_id
        ,i_item_desc
        ,revenueratio
limit 100

query.query: /* START TEMPLATE QUERY12.TPL QUERY 64 IN STREAM 0 */ /* TPC-DS QUERY12.TPL 0.64 */ SELECT I_ITEM_ID , I_ITEM_DESC , I_CATEGORY , I_CLASS , I_CURRENT_PRICE , SUM ( WS_EXT_SALES_PRICE ) AS ITEMREVENUE , SUM ( WS_EXT_SALES_PRICE ) * 100 / SUM ( SUM ( WS_EXT_SALES_PRICE ) ) OVER ( PARTITION BY I_CLASS ) AS REVENUERATIO FROM WEB_SALES , ITEM , DATE_DIM WHERE WS_ITEM_SK = I_ITEM_SK AND I_CATEGORY IN ( 'Electronics' , 'Shoes' , 'Jewelry' ) AND WS_SOLD_DATE_SK = D_DATE_SK AND D_DATE BETWEEN CAST ( '2001-06-29' AS DATE ) AND DATEADD ( DAY , 30 , CAST ( '2001-06-29' AS DATE ) ) GROUP BY I_ITEM_ID , I_ITEM_DESC , I_CATEGORY , I_CLASS , I_CURRENT_PRICE ORDER BY I_CATEGORY NULLS FIRST , I_CLASS NULLS FIRST , I_ITEM_ID NULLS FIRST , I_ITEM_DESC NULLS FIRST , REVENUERATIO NULLS FIRST LIMIT 21
